        <item>
            <title>Apple 推出 iOS 17.4　3 個重點功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/ios-17-4-3-new-feature/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios-17-4-3-new-feature</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/ios-17-4-3-new-feature/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:52:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS 17.4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[carplay]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222508</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 日前發布了 iOS 17.4 正式版，是次更新主要是為了符合歐盟《數碼市場法案》（Digintal Markets Act，DMA），另外亦更新了 CarPlay、在 Apple Podcast 加入了逐字稿（Transcript），同時亦新增不少 Emoji。現在就讓小編和大家分享一下這次 iOS 17.4 有甚麼更新重點吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222753" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709702878-267x580.jpeg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709702878-267x580.jpeg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709702878.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><h2>1. 6 個新 Emoij + 人物表情符號可向左向右</h2><p>iOS 17.4 加入了 6 個全新 Emoji，包括蘑菇、鳳凰、斷掉的鎖鏈、點頭及搖頭 Emoji。另外是次更新亦為用戶提供更多 Emoji 選項，其中有 18 款有關人物和身體的 Emoji 提供另一方向，讓用家可以自由選擇 Emoji 面向左邊抑或右邊。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028781-476x580.jpeg" alt="" width="476" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028781-476x580.jpeg 476w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028781.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 476px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點頭、搖頭 Emoji</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222758" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028783-475x580.jpeg" alt="" width="475" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028783-475x580.jpeg 475w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028783.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 475px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲蘑菇、青檸 Emoji</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg" alt="" width="480" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 480px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鳳凰、斷掉的鎖鏈 Emoji</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg" alt="" width="480" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 480px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鳳凰、斷掉的鎖鏈 Emoji</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709703260-521x580.jpeg" alt="" width="521" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709703260-521x580.jpeg 521w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709703260.jpeg 808w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 521px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲現在用家可以自由選擇部分 Emoji 面向的方向</p><h2>2. Apple Podcasts 加入逐字稿 </h2><p>iOS 17.4 更新後， Apple Podcast 加入了 Transcript（逐字稿）功能，運作原理類似 Apple Music 的歌詞般，讓用家能夠隨 Podcast 的進度，以文字形式閲讀 Podcast 的內容。目前這個功能支援英文、西班牙文、法文及德文。除了可以跟隨 Podcast 進度同步顯示逐字稿外，用家亦可一次過閲讀整篇文稿，以及搜尋特定字眼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709705270-267x580.jpeg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709705270-267x580.jpeg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709705270.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple Podcast 現時可提供逐字稿</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097052701-267x580.jpeg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097052701-267x580.jpeg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097052701.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家亦可搜尋特定字眼</p><p>Apple 表示，用家更新 iOS 17.4 後就可立即開始使用新 Podcast 功能，暫時不會提供轉譯功能，意思是如果 Podcast 本身是以英文錄製的話，Apple Podcast 暫時僅會提供英文逐字稿。</p><h2>3. CarPlay 能在儀錶板顯示 Apple 地圖資料</h2><p>iOS 17.4 之前，Apple Car Play 僅能在主螢幕顯示 Apple Map 街道方向，儀錶板則顯示導航路線概覽。現在如果駕駛者儀錶板配備顯示器的話，可以與主顯示器交替切換顯示街道視圖和路線視圖。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/carplay174-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/carplay174-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/carplay174.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2024/02/carplay-17.4.webp?resize=1536,768">9to5Mac</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/03/apple-introduces-transcripts-for-apple-podcasts">Apple</a>、<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/03/05/ios-17-4-now-available/">9to5Mac</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/apple-ios-174-can-sideload/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple iOS 17.4 九大更新重點【懶人包】開放側載、第三方可用 NFC 支付</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-3/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.4 將有第三方應用商店　開發者無需向蘋果支付額外費用</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/ios-17-4-3-new-feature/software/ios-app/">Apple 推出 iOS 17.4　3 個重點功能</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
