            <title>中電元宇宙大放送，學識減碳、完成任務拎走精美 CLP Nanobricks 模型</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/clp-tomorroverse-event/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=clp-tomorroverse-event</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/clp-tomorroverse-event/life-tech/green-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技潮人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[環保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
