            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222364</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p3">節能減碳已成為全球大趨勢，為愛地球盡一分力，環保能源將會在未來成為城市重要動力。想知道未來環保能源如何融入社會，大家可進入中電元宇宙 <a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$">CLP TomorroVerse</a> 世界更深入體驗。而現在中電更大送獎品，只要完成任務，即有機會獲得 CLP Nanobricks 模型！</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222374" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland.jpg 819w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p class="p3">中電元宇宙 <a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$">CLP TomorroVerse</a> 是一個以環保能源為動力，為動物與人類提供和諧共存的社區。裡面有不少關卡，透過精彩刺激的遊戲，讓大人小朋友都可學習未來環保能源，如何協助我們節能減碳。立即登上中電的元宇宙飛船，一齊去探險吧。</p><p>點擊活動網址進入：<a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CLP TomorroVerse</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">投入元宇宙世界三步曲</h2><p class="p3">元宇宙毋須任何數碼貨幣帳戶，你只要<a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.sandbox.game/en/experiences/TomorroVerse/0472219c-ef0f-4b0b-90d4-983cada878af/page/__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EpxRYSOw$">按此</a>打開元宇宙頁面，在 The Sandbox 內輕鬆以 Google 登入或者以電郵建立帳戶，再下載與安裝好 Sandbox 電腦版（提供 Windows/macOS 版本），即可進入中電元宇宙 CLP TomorroVerse。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01-633x580.png" alt="" width="633" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01-633x580.png 633w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01.png 982w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 633px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02-618x580.png" alt="" width="618" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02-618x580.png 618w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02.png 682w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 618px" /></a></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲The Sandbox 你只需登入 Google 帳戶或者用電郵申請帳戶，即可投入元宇宙世界（當然亦可連結電子錢包）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1-694x411.png" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1-694x411.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲在網頁上你就可建立屬於自己的分身</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1-694x428.png" alt="" width="694" height="428" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1-694x428.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1.png 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再於電腦（Windows/macOS）安裝好 The Sandbox 檔案，即可投入元宇宙世界</p><h2 class="p3">探索未來環保能源，玩任務贏禮品</h2><p class="p3">在中電元宇宙 CLP TomorroVerse 世界，大人小朋友都可一齊探索低碳生活模式。透過不同好玩任務，為愛護環境、支持環保能源出一分力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222536 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/evcar-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/evcar-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/evcar-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲你知道未來世界中，電動車的剩餘能源有甚麼用嗎?</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222538 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/visionarygallery-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/visionarygallery-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/visionarygallery-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲<span style="font-weight: 400;">在</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Visionary Gallery </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">你可參觀到過往中電活動的作品</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222539 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/solar-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/solar-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/solar-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲玩家要建設好太陽能發電設施</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222540 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/wind-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/wind-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/wind-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲為啟動元宇宙風力發電，玩家要深入海底解開機關</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222541 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fish-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fish-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fish-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲在海中暢泳與海龜、小魚作伴</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222542 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ecofun-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ecofun-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ecofun-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲<span style="font-weight: 400;">在 ECO Fun Garden 學習低碳知識</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222544 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/boat-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/boat-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/boat-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲<span style="font-weight: 400;">乘坐會飛的中電工程車回去飛船</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222393" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲參與任務可獲得不同道具</p><h2 class="p3">限時大放送<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>完成任務贏特色禮品</h2><p class="p3">馬上投入中電元宇宙 CLP TomorroVerse 探索未來能源新趨勢，現在你更可贏取 CLP Nanobricks 模型。由 2024 年 3 月 6 日起，首 100 名完成所有任務並填寫好表格的參加者，將獲得造型可愛而設計精緻的 CLP Nanobricks 模型*（款式包括男工程師、女工程師，及中電緊急服務工程車。款式將隨機發送）。</p><p class="p3">把握機會，馬上按此輕鬆投入中電元宇宙，贏取特色禮品吧！</p><p>點擊活動網址進入：<a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CLP TomorroVerse</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-694x511.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="511" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-694x511.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-scaled.jpg 1223w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222396" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-694x538.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="538" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-694x538.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-scaled.jpg 1161w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8492-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222394" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8492-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8492-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8492-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p3">*記住留意，限時活動僅限於香港玩家 ! 玩家將會在 21 天內於參加表格上的電郵地址收到獎品換領確認訊息 (若沒有收到電郵，意即未能得到換領資格)。每位玩家只能贏取禮品一次。重複的玩家或 The Sandbox 帳戶將不獲考慮。</p><p><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/meta-optimistic-apple-vision-pro-launch/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">對 Apple Vision Pro 感到樂觀   Meta 期望藉此活化頭戴裝置市場</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/clp-tomorroverse-event/life-tech/green-2/">中電元宇宙大放送，學識減碳、完成任務拎走精美 CLP Nanobricks 模型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
