                <![CDATA[<p>現時 FB IG 及 X 都不能進入，FB 則是戶口密碼錯誤的狀態, 連 Whatsapp 也有報告出現不穩定的問題。youtube 則運作正常。小編也試過經使用多國 VPN 也未能解決問題，相信不是地區性封鎖。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1222668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240305115919-694x466.png" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240305115919-694x466.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240305115919.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1222667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240305115541-694x423.png" alt="" width="694" height="423" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240305115541-694x423.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240305115541.png 1178w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/08/default-end-to-end-encryption-fb-messenger/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Facebook Messenger 宣佈，所有通訊預設點對點加密</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/fb-ig-x-dead/life-tech/social-network/">FB、IG、X (Twitter) 、WhatsApp 及 Threads 等美國社交網大死機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
